[l] Oha, The Jewish Cronicle holt die Antisemitismuskeule gegen Corbyn raus:But in this rare instance we are certain that we speak for the vast majority of British Jews in expressing deep foreboding at the prospect of Mr Corbyn’s election as Labour leader.Because, although there is no direct evidence that he has an issue himself with Jews, there is overwhelming evidence of his association with, support for — and even in one case, alleged funding of — Holocaust deniers, terrorists and some outright antisemites.Die Vorwuerfe gehen von Spenden an extremistische Organisationen bis hin zu der Behauptung, er wuerde Hamas und Hisbollah als seine Freunde bezeichnen. Da wird der Corbyn wohl ein paar Dinge zu erklaeren haben. (Danke, Andreas)
